left/right shift string.

e.g. n=8 and i=3, "abcdefgh" => "defghabc"


algorithm 1 (strshift.c):
reverse(0,i-1)  (=> cbadefgh)
reverse(i,n-1)  (=> cbahgfed)
reverse(0,n-1)  (=> defghabc)

algorithm 2 (strshift2.c):
k = 0; save str[0] to temp, move str[3] to str[0], str[6] to str[3], str[0] to str[6]
k = 1; save str[1] to temp, move str[4] to str[1], str[7] to str[4], str[1] to str[7]
k = 2; save str[2] to temp, move str[5] to str[2], str[8] to str[5], str[2] to str[8]

